sections.content:
We use Personal Information for purposes including:

- Providing and maintaining our Services;
- Improving our Services and conducting research;
- Communicating with you about our Services;
- Preventing fraud, protecting security, and complying with legal obligations;
- Aggregating or de-identifying data for research and analytics.

We may disclose your Personal Information to:

- Service Providers: For assistance in providing and maintaining our Services;
- Business Transfers: In connection with mergers, acquisitions, or other corporate transactions;
- Legal Obligations: To comply with legal requirements or protect our rights and users;
- Affiliates: For uses consistent with this Privacy Policy.

Depending on your location, you may have the right to:

- Access your Personal Information;
- Request deletion or correction of your Personal Information;
- Object to the processing of your Personal Information;
- Withdraw consent where processing is based on consent.

You can exercise these rights by contacting us at [contact information].
